  "33 - Wheel tones check": {
   "width": 12060,
   "height": 9060,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "1st STEP: Choose the wheel to check",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 330,
      "width": 3900
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2nd STEP: Push the \"Start counting\" button",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3480,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 5580
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3rd STEP: After turning the wheel for exactly 1 turn, without going backwards, read the result",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 345,
      "width": 10560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Move the mark on the wheel for about 1 cm.",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 6720,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Strart again from step 1",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 6960,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "B ==> If the first result is less than 47 tones and if the second result is less than 48 tones, then the tone wheel is faulty and must be changed",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 7320,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "C ==> If the result is over 48 tones, more than 1 exact turn has been performed; Start over from step 1.",
     "color": "rgb(255,128,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 0,
      "top": 7920,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 12120
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ">>>",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 5280,
      "top": 5280,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
